  <span id="freeText1995709395904467050" style="display:none">This book takes place on the Island of Sicily. Mrs. Pollifax is sent to assist an ex-CIA agent, an art gallery owner on the trail of a Julius Caesar document with signature. His job is to authenticate the document prior to being purchased by the person hiring him.<br /><br />Upon arriving Mrs, P is met by another agent and taken to meet her contact. From here on it gets alternately funny,and sometimes unclear just who is who and what is going on. Alternately being tailed, shot at and then stormed at the gates of the place they stayed at, all becomes clear.<br /><br />Action is ongoing, lies are many, truths are hidden but in the end Mrs. P completes her mission and has fun using her Karate.</span>
