<div id="review_3808226211" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3808226211" />
    <a title="Sandra Allen" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/57810083-sandra-allen"><img alt="Sandra Allen" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3808226211?book_show_action=true">Jan 31, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sandra Allen" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sandra Allen" href="/user/show/57810083-sandra-allen">Sandra Allen</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/50658423-mrs-pollifax-and-the-second-thief">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3808226211" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8025166869362692474"><strong>Mrs. Pollifax draws us into intrigue, rescues an old friend, and joins forces to catch an assassin. </strong><br/><br/>Mrs. Pollifax answers a mayday call from retired CIA thief, Farrell. He has recognized the assassin, Aristotle, in Sicily. Not serving life in prison. From the time Emily’s plane lands, she is dodging attempts on her life. An agent, Kate, delivers Emily and Farrell to her aunt’s villa for safety. Farrell has been shot. A lively new cast of characters, romance and mysteries even at the villa keep t</span>
  <span id="freeText8025166869362692474" style="display:none"><strong>Mrs. Pollifax draws us into intrigue, rescues an old friend, and joins forces to catch an assassin. </strong><br /><br />Mrs. Pollifax answers a mayday call from retired CIA thief, Farrell. He has recognized the assassin, Aristotle, in Sicily. Not serving life in prison. From the time Emily’s plane lands, she is dodging attempts on her life. An agent, Kate, delivers Emily and Farrell to her aunt’s villa for safety. Farrell has been shot. A lively new cast of characters, romance and mysteries even at the villa keep the you turning pages. The conclusion is unexpected even for fans who have read all of the books. One of the best in the series. </span>
  <a data-text-id="8025166869362692474" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
